queries.sql: select DISTINCT title,c1t.code,c1titleID,c1.remarks,(select COUNT(*) from tbl_client_files_c1 WHERE tbl_client_files_c1.c1tID = c1.c1tID and tbl_client_files_c1.workpaper = 4 and tbl_client_files_c1.clientID = 5) as x , (select COUNT(*) from tbl_client_files_c1 WHERE tbl_client_files_c1.c1tID = c1.c1tID and tbl_client_files_c1.workpaper = 4 and tbl_client_files_c1.clientID = 5 and `updated_on` IS NOT NULL) as y from tbl_c1_titles as c1t, tbl_client_files_c1 as c1 where c1t.c1titleID = c1.c1tID and c1.clientID = 5 and c1.workpaper = 4 and c1.status = 'Preparing'
